\v 9 Dios mi' lu' ts'ÊŒctisan jini tsa'ix bÊŒ yÊŒlÊŒ. Jini ti' pÊŒyÊŒyetla cha'an mi la' wajÃ±el yic'ot i Yalobil Jesucristo lac Yum.   
\s1 Cha'an contrajiya cha'an ti' t'oxoyob i bÊŒ jini ochemo' bÊŒ ti' t'an Dios  
