\v 2 Ti jujump'ej Ã±axan bÊŒ q'uin ti semana jujuntiquiletla yom mi la' parte lot tyaq'uin ti la' wotyot. JiÃ±ÊŒch bajche' yonlel ti la' ganari tyaq'uin mi la' loc'san ts'itya' cha'an ofrenda. Jini on bÊŒ ti ganari mÃ¡s mero on yom i yÊŒc'. Jini mach'ÊŒ on ti' ganari, mÃ¡s ts'itya' jach yom i yÊŒc'. Che' jini ma'ix mi la' wersa much'quin ba' bÊŒ ora mij c'otyel.   
\p
\v 3 Che' mij c'otyel mi quejel j choque' majlel ti JerusalÃ©n jini hermaÃ±ujob mu' bÊŒ la' yajcan. Mi quejel cÊŒq'ueÃ±ob jun cha'an i ch'ÊŒmob majlel yic'ot jini tyaq'uin chÊŒncol bÊŒ la' much'quin cha'an mi yÊŒq'ueÃ±ob jini hermaÃ±ujob ya'i.   
\p
\v 4 Ch'ujbiyic c majlel quic'ot, mic majlel quic'ot jini mu' bÊŒ quejel la' choque' majlel.   
\s1 Ba' yom i majlel Pablo  
\p
\v 5 Che' mic majlel cula'aÃ±etla, Ã±axan com Ã±umel ti paÃ±imil Macedonia bÊŒ i c'aba'. Che' jini ti wi'il mij c'otyel ya' ba' aÃ±etla.   
