\v 19 Jini ochemo' bÊŒ ti' t'an Dios mu' bÊŒ i much'quiÃ±ob i bÊŒ ya' ti paÃ±imil Asia bÊŒ i c'aba' mi' chocbeÃ±etla tyÊŒlel saludos. Aquila yic'ot yijÃ±am Priscila bÊŒ i c'aba' yic'ot jini ochemo' bÊŒ ti' t'an Dios mu' bÊŒ i much'quiÃ±ob i bÊŒ ti yotyot mi' wen chocbeÃ±etla tyÊŒlel saludos cha'an ti lac Yum.   
